description: Exploring the humorous dynamics between a gossipy water drop and a methodical printer.
title: Office Secrets
n_1: Leaky shares the latest gossip with Printy at the water cooler.
n_2: Leaky, the center of attention, whispers to a group of office supplies.
n_3: Printy, overwhelmed by the overload of information, struggles to keep up.
n_4: In a chaotic finale, Printy jams, and Leaky overflows with laughter.
c1_1: You won't believe what I heard today!
c1_2: And then, guess what happened next?
c2_3: I am not designed for this!
c1_4: This is why we can't have secrets here!
c2_4: I'm literally jammed because of your leaks!
